{"tid":652041,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"你地明點解DC狗叫DC狗啦，每個Marvel post都要入去撩交哎","createTime":"2018-05-03T14:26:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T12:30:51.000Z","uid":159798,"like":29,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"415b677a86fe4217595c4d97cd79184f8bdd1861","tid":652041,"uid":159798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T14:26:11.000Z","msg":"正字又嘈一餐，明明係地道廣東話<br />\n<br />\n票房高又話搞彎電影業，星戰仲高啦<br />\n<br />\n讚親Marvel角色都要搬返小丑出黎<br />\n冇人唔認同，但唔駛人地一有戲就重覆講掛？<br />\n<br />\n踩Marvel冇深度，懶清高好冇品<br />\n你有冷門好戲咪開post介紹俾連登仔囉<br />\n<br />\n呢期上大作高票房，多人討論多人讚好正常姐<br />\n成日屈人打手，又話霸住影視台<br />\n唔通要多數人讓路俾少數人？<br />\n<br />\n以上講嘅事例，來來去去都係嗰幾個user name<br />\n好啦我以為真係清高撚深度撚正義撚<br />\n屌，轉個頭入DC post又見返嗰幾個名<br />\n係咪要cap晒圖開晒名先識收手呀？"},{"pid":"a1bc3703429403e1fe76055d1ef500dec8ba0664","tid":652041,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T14:56:22.000Z","msg":"開名囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d925ea3ed68fb2b594dd2c69f2a4df412e688ea","tid":652041,"uid":139671,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T06:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/145529_4f853c2bf20972b8fe1b3feec089ca5d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F145529_4f853c2bf20972b8fe1b3feec089ca5d.png&h=3aea5602&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f2d16d02aeb214aed9f2e1e46191d433a36ec1e9","tid":652041,"uid":96964,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T07:01:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/150106_2c40a30dfd9ef65529678cac0f43e312.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F150106_2c40a30dfd9ef65529678cac0f43e312.png